00:37:05.740 --> 00:37:07.030
DREW PHILP: Sure.

00:37:07.030 --> 00:37:10.120
The school system
is trash, obviously.

00:37:10.120 --> 00:37:14.550
And I do see people,
younger folks with kids,

00:37:14.550 --> 00:37:15.460
starting to stay.

00:37:15.460 --> 00:37:16.810
That was always the big thing.

00:37:16.810 --> 00:37:19.180
That was the tipping point
for where the city was--

00:37:19.180 --> 00:37:20.889
