figure this question out.

00:37:50.200 --> 00:37:53.520
Another one is the
Waldorf School.

00:37:53.520 --> 00:37:56.020
Lots of my friends send their
children to the Waldorf School

00:37:56.020 --> 00:37:57.030
there.

00:37:57.030 --> 00:37:57.934
It is happening.

00:37:57.934 --> 00:37:59.350
I don't think,
unfortunately, it's

00:37:59.350 --> 00:38:01.900
