00:38:20.354 --> 00:38:22.660
People come from all
over the world to see--

00:38:22.660 --> 00:38:26.560
in Germany and Belgium,
it's called Detroit music.

00:38:26.560 --> 00:38:27.590
We invented it.

00:38:27.590 --> 00:38:30.010
It's one of our cultural icons.

00:38:30.010 --> 00:38:32.710
And I think, actually, we
could do a whole lot more

00:38:32.710 --> 00:38:35.470
