music in Detroit.

00:38:35.470 --> 00:38:38.440
And it's a big, huge deal.

00:38:38.440 --> 00:38:40.540
And it came from here.

00:38:40.540 --> 00:38:43.510
I'm not a huge electronic
music fan myself,

00:38:43.510 --> 00:38:46.210
