beautiful out of it.

00:39:01.780 --> 00:39:04.984
I actually think, in Detroit,
we could do a whole lot more

00:39:04.984 --> 00:39:05.650
to support that.

00:39:05.650 --> 00:39:10.330
There's kids like Kyle Hall, who
is another Detroit artist you

00:39:10.330 --> 00:39:15.520
